title: is_maildir()
brief: Test whether a given path represents a Maildir.
seealso: executable, file_exists, load_directory, is_directory, create_maildir, delete_maildir
version: 0.17
----

<p>This function tests whether the specified path is a Maildir folder.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
if ( is_maildir( os.getenv( "HOME" ) .. "/Maildir" ) ) then
   <a href="/lua/maildir_prefix.html">maildir_prefix</a>( os.getenv( "HOME" ) .. "/Maildir" );
end
</pre>
